Post.title: JavaScript 102
Post.author: Hans Lee
Post.content:
JavaScript is essential to companies using Node.js. Its THE language of year 2016. However, it is also a fragile language could be easily abused.

Road toward clean code (less bug)

Function.prototype.call

slice call

To convert an array-like object to an array, use Array#slice.

arguments property

trigger arguments

The arguments object is an Array-like object corresponding to the arguments passed to a function.

function argument 0,1,2,3, index

call

The call() method calls a function with a given this value and arguments provided individually.

call

call thisArg .bind(this) call this

call

2 context bind animals print

happy coding, may the code will always be with you~
